synopsis: Elegant, retired architect Shauna (70) crosses paths with Pierre, a happily married doctor in his 40s, who first made an impression on her in a brief meeting 15 years previously. Both are quite troubled to meet again and begin an affair. While Pierre’s family life is soon turned upside down, Shauna struggles with feelings she thought belonged to the past.

synopsis: 6 Films of legendary russian animation master Yuriy Norshteyn  are now fully 2K restored in Steelbook! Blu-ray&DVD

Rocky is down and out on his luck and about to be kicked out of his house. He goes to a talented sensei for help and learns the ways of rock paper scissors. He is confident of his skills and challenges the world-renowned Kim Jong Un to get his life back on track.
One woman's journey for self-discovery and turns into a harrowing tale of survival.
